verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Sanghame shareeram shareerame sangham divya
Drustaanthamulatho nindinadi devuni illaayana
Nivaasa stalam naveena varudu raaja nagaramu illu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Intiki punaadhi aadhaara mainatlu draakshavallilo
Theegelu nilchunatlu nara shareramunaku
Thalavale bhaaryaku bharthavale kristunugala{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Saarvathrika sabhanu kaanagaleni kaaranaana saitaanu
Kalavaramu nonde stala sanghamu dwaara
Saarvathrika maina sanghamunu joopa veelagu nijamu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Maru janma mondina vaare ee sanghamu asamaanu
Desude yaddaani shiramu yogyamugaa naidu sevala
Jethumu mudamuna paadumu yesuku Halleluya{/lang-eng}
